{
  "stem": "4700.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But definitely I, I look at things-- material things don't matter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's, it's the human relations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so, I think so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm pretty sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're not-- not materialistic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they don't have to have designer jeans or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, because we live in a very materialistic culture.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they are very modest and their wives, also, of the similar ilk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I don't-- I mean, if you have it, you have it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you don't have it, you don't have it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't judge people by--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--What they have or what they achieved, whether they've got high position or not.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it doesn't, doesn't matter to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm a voluntary guide at the museum.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was active-- there was a children, I think, I can't remember what it was called, at the Great Synagogue-- there was an exhibition.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was active in that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there was the 'Children of the Holocaust,' which was opened at the War Memorial in Canberra, which was quite an unprecedented step for the War Memorial to take.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was a voluntary guide there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had, I think, two guides, twice a week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We manned the exhibition.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was there for the opening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was active in that, because I remembered quite a lot, having been there for three years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And also I knew quite a few of the girls that drew those pictures, so--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a picture-- there is in Prague, there is a collection of drawings, made by the children in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What happened, the children were not allowed to be taught.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was done secretly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were allowed to learn drawing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans permitted that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at, at some stage there were quite a lot of children.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
